data.name: label_help.Text
data.value:
Here are some sorts of advice which could help you while you are using our soft:
At first, you have to create an account:
There are two different accounts you can create. The first one is free, but you are not able to write more than 10 ToDoLists
The other one is premium and costs 10$ per months and you can write up to 50 ToDoLists
